channel.title: | Project Zero | No silabs! | A REAL RS2 Private Server |
channel.description:
[i]Hello Moparscape,yes it has been a while :P I am rs w00dcut BTW I was taking a break and decided to come back and post a new source,I'm sick of seeing all these Jagex/Silabs items. If you want to play REAL RUNESCAPE GO TO REAL RUNESCAPE. I don't know about you guys but I miss the old private servers,Mopar was amazing when they had an advertisement section. When they cleared,I lost some of my favorite Servers:[/i] [u]Zamorakscape Blakscape Fr33sc4p3 pkz[/u]--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [i]Anyways,here is my non-silab server.Basically started from scratch,had some files in it,I had to add alot.[/i]--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [code]//Start of commands by rs w00dcut\\ Admin Commands
::pickup ::Tele Coord1 Coord2 ::xrichie(Gives Max Cash) ::Master ::pure(Like master but pure stats) ::adminzone(Blank spot,Do whatever you want)
Player Commands:
::Home(Takes you home) ::praise(Maxes Prayer) ::food ::arrows ::starter(Can only use once) ::dive(Gives Fishbowl Helm + Apparatus) ::axe(To wc) ::willows(WC) ::maples(WC) ::mages(WC) ::pk(Only place you can PK) ::monsters(NPC Training)
//End of Commands\\ [/code]
